34:50.520 --> 34:54.581
Trust me,
we're not gettin' on.

34:54.620 --> 34:57.214
We're just
gettin' through.

35:01.830 --> 35:04.321
Stella.

35:04.370 --> 35:06.326
Stella...?

35:06.370 --> 35:09.089
Hey! Hey! Hey!

35:10.270 --> 35:12.261
Hey.

35:12.310 --> 35:15.529
- What's wrong?
