Yep.

35:49.410 --> 35:52.277
- ( beeps )
- Hello.

35:52.310 --> 35:55.916
Hi, Mr. Oliver.

35:55.950 --> 35:58.714
What kind of incident?

36:00.950 --> 36:02.383
Okay.

36:02.420 --> 36:04.627
No, I'm--
I'm on my way.

