avoiding my calls?

38:19.130 --> 38:22.395
Remy:
Trust me, Charley.
He feels like hell.

38:22.430 --> 38:24.694
Okay? It was
an honest mistake.

38:24.730 --> 38:27.858
So, you'd make
that mistake?

38:27.900 --> 38:29.663
Well...

38:29.700 --> 38:31.736
