40:02.600 --> 40:04.522
I'm sorry, Rah.

40:10.570 --> 40:12.561
You were right.

40:12.610 --> 40:14.976
I should have been there
more for you.

40:27.020 --> 40:30.057
I read your article.

40:30.090 --> 40:32.024
It was dope.

40:34.560 --> 40:36.050
I'm gonna be around
more to help.

40:36.100 --> 40:38.193
Mm-hmm.

40:38.230 --> 40:39.959
